sub_title: {On parental leave till August 21st } - Culture,Trends & Insights | Strategic & Creative Solutions
summary:
I guide brands to relevant and aspirational playgrounds and help them connect with their audience culturally and emotionally. By blending observation, research, strategy, creative thinking, and intuition, I unearth actionable insights and translate them into tailored provocations, unexpected ideas, and inspiring perspectives. Passionate about inclusivity and representation I will always make sure to bring those important topics to the table.

You can see some samples of my work here : 
www.nastassjabonnabel.com

For further information & more details, please contact me at bonjour@nastassjabonnabel.com
